You should generate your password and store it with a password manager.

* Password must be 16 or longer
* At least one uppercase letter
* At least one lowercase letter
* At least one digit
* At least one special character
* No username in any form
* No monotonic character sequences longer than 3
* No consecutive character longer than 2
* No words from the GECOS field

Note that you will need to change your password every {{ pass_max_days }} days.
